'''''Roma wa la n'toura''''' (Icyongereza: '''''Rome Rather Than You'''''; Igifaransa: '''''Rome plutôt que vous''''' ) ni filime y’ikinamico yo muri 2006 yakorewe muri [[Alijeriya]]-[[Igifaransa|abafaransa]] [[Ubudage|n’Ubudage]] iyobowe na Tariq Teguia  ikinwamo na Samira Kaddour na Rachid Amrani nk’urubyiruko babiri bashaka kuva muri Alijeriya n'intambara y'abenegihugu ya Alijeriya kugira ngo bagire ejo hazaza heza.  Nibikorwa bya Teguia byerekanwe bwa mbere.  (Yabanje gukora filime ngufi na documentaire ya 2002.  ) Filime yatsindiye igihembo cyihariye cyabacamanza mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya firime rya Friborg 2007. 

== Umugambi ==
Kamel w'imyaka 20 n'inshuti ye, Zina w'imyaka makumyabiri n'itatu, bashakisha muri [[Alijeriya]] Bosco ucuruza abantu  kugira ngo babone pasiporo mpimbano kugira ngo bashobore kuva mu gihugu berekeza i Roma.

== Kwakira ==
''Abanenga ibinyamakuru bitandukanye,'' Robert Koehler yashimye "Umukinnyi wa mbere wa Tariq Teguia. . . Nubwo ibihe bya nyuma biteganijwe, kugerayo ndetse na nyuma yacyo byerekana Teguia kuba umuyobozi w’amasezerano akomeye ".  Koehler yemeje kandi "ibihangano bisanzwe, byoroshye imikorere" ya Kaddoui na Amrani. <ref name="Variety" /> Mu ''kinyamakuru Slant'', ariko, Eric Henderson yabonaga ko iyi filime "yatekerejwe mu bwirasi, yiyitirira ko yakozwe, kandi ikaba ndende". 

